{"tid":1362090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑示威影響拳賽收入 34歲泰國拳手涉收錢暴打示威者","createTime":"2019-07-24T18:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T08:27:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":91,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"86c79929f8098e8a76e55fdf0788004823096162","tid":1362090,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:43:27.000Z","msg":"一名泰國拳手涉嫌參與周日晚元朗西鐵站的恐怖襲擊事件，暴打車站周圍路人和車站內及列車上的乘客。<br />\n曾擔任路透社駐泰國通訊員的蘇格蘭記者馬歇爾(Andrew MacGregor Marshall)在Facebook上說，他從照片中認出襲擊民眾的白衣暴徒中，其中一人是34歲泰國拳手Arthit Ruenpech。<br />\n有人猜測香港近日的逆權示威活動，影響到原先安排的拳賽，令泰國拳手失去不菲收入，因而被招攬行兇。泰國傳媒又指立法會議員何君堯相信有份策劃元朗恐襲。泰國國家安全委員會確認Arthit與新蒲崗一間拳館有連繫。<br />\n香港有網民指Arthit來港多年，他被泰國觀眾認出身份後，被泰國記者追問，最後承認受僱持棍暴打香港市民。<br />\nThe National Thailand"},{"pid":"88966ecd316ef361ad5f157fb96cac0ef7b9eabb","tid":1362090,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:43:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1342382/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1342382/</a>"},{"pid":"2e21dd4606fc1ff215c5eaedf7ad80dc6fd5d60c","tid":1362090,"uid":121546,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:46:39.000Z","msg":"屌你老母走去外國打人<br />\n唔好比佢返鄉下"},{"pid":"6901f20fd4b4dfd5b67bc0008647cbe3796c169b","tid":1362090,"uid":67237,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:50:24.000Z","msg":"學曾志偉講句，仆你個街仆你個街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aaaee686a6e1ce4ffc78592e04425fc0f28c01a","tid":1362090,"uid":103230,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:51:59.000Z","msg":"泰國都知係何君堯<br />\n<br />\n香港警察唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab2f2ebaa15efb34bf0ea17a90d1326c777ad2d","tid":1362090,"uid":186071,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0